18 ʹ Slender larva; sides of pronotum parallel and slightly concave. Front pronotal corners a little extended; abdominal fringes of slender pale hairs with tips curved against body; paraproct caudally narrowed, obliquely truncate, inner edge blending into a long, upcurved spine; micropterous (
